    {
      "id": "youtube-class-editor-view",
      "type": "view",
      "label": "Editor View (editor.web)",
      "position": {
        "x": 20,
        "y": -80
      },
      "width": 420,
      "height": 260,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "view": {
          "intent": "editor",
          "payload": "editor.web"
        },
        "editor": {
          "web": {
            "fields": [
              {
                "key": "videoId",
                "label": "YouTube Video ID",
                "type": "text",
                "path": "data.videoId",
                "placeholder": "dQw4w9WgXcQ"
              },
              {
                "key": "title",
                "label": "Embed Title",
                "type": "text",
                "path": "data.title",
                "placeholder": "YouTube video player"
              },
              {
                "key": "startSeconds",
                "label": "Start At (seconds)",
                "type": "number",
                "path": "data.startSeconds",
                "placeholder": "0"
              },
              {
                "key": "autoplay",
                "label": "Autoplay",
                "type": "boolean",
                "path": "data.autoplay"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "youtube-class-notes",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Definition Notes",
      "position": {
        "x": 20,
        "y": 220
      },
      "width": 880,
      "height": 260,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## YouTube Embedded Node\n\nUse this node type by adding a dictionary entry in your host graph:\n\n- `key`: `youtube-embedded`\n- `ref`: `/library/classes/nodes/youtube-embedded.node`\n\nThen create nodes of type `youtube-embedded` with data:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"videoId\": \"dQw4w9WgXcQ\",\n  \"title\": \"YouTube video player\",\n  \"startSeconds\": 0,\n  \"autoplay\": false\n}\n```"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "youtube-class-node-view-detail",
      "type": "view",
      "label": "Node View (node.web.detail)",
      "position": {
        "x": 470,
        "y": -80
      },
      "width": 430,
      "height": 260,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "view": {
          "intent": "node",
          "payload": "node.web.detail",
          "controls": [
            {
              "id": "youtube-edit",
              "type": "button",
              "label": "Edit",
              "icon": "edit",
              "variant": "outlined",
              "priority": "high",
              "action": "openEditor"
            }
          ]
        },
        "node": {
          "web": {
            "detail": {
              "html": "<div style='width:100%;height:100%;display:flex;flex-direction:column;box-sizing:border-box;overflow:hidden;background:transparent;'>\n  <div style='font:600 12px system-ui, sans-serif;opacity:.8;margin:0 0 6px 0;'>{{label}}</div>\n  <div style='flex:1;min-height:0;'>\n    <iframe\n      title='{{data.title}}'\n      src='https://www.youtube.com/embed/{{data.videoId}}?start={{data.startSeconds}}&autoplay={{data.autoplay}}&rel=0'\n      width='100%'\n      height='100%'\n      frameborder='0'\n      allow='accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share'\n      referrerpolicy='strict-origin-when-cross-origin'\n      allowfullscreen\n      style='border:0;border-radius:8px;display:block;background:transparent;'></iframe>\n  </div>\n</div>"
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "youtube-class-node-view-summary",
      "type": "view",
      "label": "Node View (node.web.summary)",
      "position": {
        "x": 470,
        "y": 220
      },
      "width": 430,
      "height": 260,
